snippet.title: Phasmophobia - Official Xbox Release Date Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview October 2024
snippet.description:
The genre defining horror game is finally coming to Xbox. Get ready for spine-chilling ghost hunts solo or with up to three friends this Halloween season as Phasmophobia comes to Xbox Series X|S on October 29, 2024. Gather your equipment, investigate the paranormal and join the already almost 20 million player base, with cross play supported from day one. Available to wishlist now: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/Phasmophobia/9N6D60SBZN05

SUBSCRIBE TO XBOX: https://xbx.lv/2EEjmaR
